109.Name: MargaRATa
109.name: MargaRATa
109.description:
MargaRATa Monday! Here's how to mix up one of your own:

- 1oz tequila
-1oz triple sec
-2oz lime juice
-2oz orange juice
- 0.5oz jalapeno simple syrup
- A couple shakes of Tajin

Shake it all up, serve it in a salt and tajin rimmed glass over ice.
